 other energies that $\\Gamma$- converge to the Griffith fracture energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Nov 2014 19:55:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Nov 2014 00:08:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 11 Dec 2014 20:00:23 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 2015 18:42:25 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 13 Jul 2015 14:02:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-14"}
