. We predict that the cross-correlation of their data will allow a\nmeasurement of the DM mass with an uncertainty of a factor of 1.5-2, even for\nmoderate subhalo boosts, for DM masses up to few hundreds of GeV and thermal\nannihilation rates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Nov 2014 21:00:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Nov 2015 14:42:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-25"}
