d indicates how they may serve as a\nbuffer against other evolutionary forces such as genetic drift and selection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Nov 2014 06:47:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Feb 2015 09:09:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 4 May 2016 12:21:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-10"}
